loadout-timer-overall-too-high = You need [color=yellow]{ TOSTRING($time, "0") }[/color] minutes less overall game time
loadout-timer-role-insufficient = You lack [color=yellow]{ TOSTRING($time, "0") }[/color] minutes of game time in the [color={ $departmentColor }]{ $job }[/color] position
